}

.sidebar-freedom-wall-cta:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(234, 179, 56, 0.18), rgba(255, 204, 51, 0.12));
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(234, 179, 56, 0.15);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
}
```

**From collection.css** - Gradient headers:
```css
.collection-gradient-header[data-accent="0"] {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B8F71, #4a7a52);  /* Sage */
}
.collection-gradient-header[data-accent="1"] {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D4A853, #C4943E);  /* Gold */
}
.collection-gradient-header[data-accent="2"] {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #...); /* Various */
}
```

#### C. Animation Patterns

**From collection.css**:
```css
